{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/jakarta-titik-nol-ancaman-maut-dari-lautan/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Jakarta Titik Nol: Ancaman Maut Dari Lautan","content":"\n<p>Sebagai ibu kota negara Indonesia, kota Jakarta memiliki\nbanyak permasalahan, mulai dari jumlah populasi hingga sampah dan banjir. Belum\nlagi ditambah posisi kota Jakarta yang cukup rawan gempa dan tsunami secara\ngeografis. Jika tidak ada upaya yang tepat untuk mengatasinya, ancaman-ancaman\nini akan memakan korban dengan cepat. Hal inilah yang jadi fokus utama dalam\nJakarta Titik Nol, komik terbaru dari CIAYO Comics.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Jakarta Titik Nol merupakan komik dengan cerita yang\ndikarang oleh Revin Putra, Dhanie Ramadhan, serta Snow Rexilium. Ilustrasi\nkomik ini diserahkan kepada Twelveink Studio yang terdiri dari storyboarder\nSamuel, line artist Chandra, dan colorist Arzul.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54089\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/jakarta-titik-nol-ancaman-maut-dari-lautan/attachment/01-jakarta-titik-nol/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-jakarta-titik-nol\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-jakarta-titik-nol-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" alt=\"Mesjid Istiqlal dilanda tsunami. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54089\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-jakarta-titik-nol-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Mesjid Istiqlal dilanda tsunami. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam Jakarta Titik Nol, kamu bisa menyaksikan bagaimana\nkota Jakarta porak poranda akibat bencana gempa, badai, dan tsunami yang\nterjadi secara bersamaan. Banyak orang terjebak di gedung-gedung tinggi dan\nmenunggu pertolongan. Salah satunya adalah Bram dan Putri, dua pegawai gudang\nyang juga harus berlindung di tempat kerja mereka. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54090\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/jakarta-titik-nol-ancaman-maut-dari-lautan/attachment/02-jakarta-titik-nol/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-jakarta-titik-nol\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-jakarta-titik-nol-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" alt=\"Bertahan hidup dengan segala cara. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54090\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/02-jakarta-titik-nol-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Bertahan hidup dengan segala cara. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Situasi semakin tidak menentu saat suhu udara menurun dan\ntipisnya persediaan makanan. Beruntung, Bram sebelumnya punya pengalaman\nsebagai pemadam kebakaran sehingga ia pun memimpin proses pencarian makanan di bagian\nkantor yang tidak terjamah banjir. Namun, bukan hanya gempa dan banjir saja\nyang menjadi tantangan bagi mereka. Karena ternyata, mereka tidak sendirian di\ndekat genangan airâ€¦</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54091\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/jakarta-titik-nol-ancaman-maut-dari-lautan/attachment/03-jakarta-titik-nol/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-jakarta-titik-nol\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-jakarta-titik-nol-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" alt=\"Jakarta Titik Nol tampilkan serangkaian musibah beruntun. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54091\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/03-jakarta-titik-nol-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Jakarta Titik Nol tampilkan serangkaian musibah beruntun. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Jakarta Titik Nol merupakan komik horor thriller yang\nmengangkat tema disaster dan survival. Mungkin saat melihat gambar banner di\natas kamu bakal teringat film-film disaster serupa seperti Snakes on a Plane\natau Sharknado. Tapi jangan kuatir karena Jakarta Titik Nol nggak bakal\nse-corny dua film tersebut.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54092\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/jakarta-titik-nol-ancaman-maut-dari-lautan/attachment/04-jakarta-titik-nol/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-jakarta-titik-nol\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" alt=\"Keegoisan manusia akan menjadi senjata makan tuan. Sumber: CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-54092\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-jakarta-titik-nol-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Keegoisan manusia akan menjadi senjata makan tuan. Sumber: CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Membaca Jakarta Titik Nol membuatmu seakan tidak diberi\nruang untuk bernafas. Setiap chapter dan panel selalu punya cerita menegangkan.\nBaik Bram dan Putri selalu dihadapkan pada berbagai ancaman dan marabahaya.\nApalagi karena Putri juga membawa keponakannya Chika ke kantor. Bram, Putri,\ndan para penyintas lainnya harus bekerja sama dan menanggalkan ego mereka untuk\nbisa bertahan hidup dari segala ancaman.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"54093\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/jakarta-titik-nol-ancaman-maut-dari-lautan/attachment/05-jakarta-titik-nol/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/05-jakarta-titik-nol.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-jakarta-titik-nol\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\